{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Crust","content":["Preheat oven to 170°C. Set aside a rectangular fluted tart tin (34 x 13 cm).","Place almonds into mixing bowl and mill <b>10 sec\/speed 7<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place coconut oil into mixing bowl and melt <b>2 min\/50°C\/speed 2<b>.","Add syrup, eggs and vanilla and mix <b>5 sec\/speed 4<b>.","Add coconut flour, salt, baking powder and reserved almonds and mix <b>5 sec\/speed 7<b> until dough forms.","Press dough into bottom and sides of prepared tin then prick base with a fork. Bake for 13-15 minutes (170°C) until lightly golden. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Set aside tart case to cool. Reduce oven to 140°C."]},{"title":"Filling","content":["Place butter into mixing bowl and melt <b>2 min\/50°C\/speed 2<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place eggs and sugar into mixing bowl and mix <b>1 min\/speed 4<b>.","Add lemon juice, orange juice and melted butter and mix <b>1 min\/speed 4<b>.","Set aside for 10 minutes, then carefully skim off and discard any foam that has formed on surface.","Pour mixture into reserved crust and bake for 25-30 minutes (140°C) until set (filling will still have slight wobble in the centre). Allow to cool completely in tin (approx. 1 hour). Remove from tin and place onto a serving plate, before serving with cream (optional)."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Crust","content":["30 g blanched almonds","100 g coconut oil","90 g pure maple syrup","2 eggs","1 tsp natural vanilla extract","90 g coconut flour","¼ tsp salt","½ tsp gluten free baking powder (see Tips)"]},{"title":"Filling","content":["110 g unsalted butter","4 eggs","150 g caster sugar","100 g lemon juice (approx. 3 lemons)","50 g orange juice (approx. 1 large orange)","pouring (whipping) cream, to serve (optional)"]}],"id":"r114656","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-4bERi7-yNY4\/XZWpudF04rI\/AAAAAAAAfOA\/U8cGiZDSd4EgLBZ5zCzBl-YIcPUQbw07QCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_47DuWMdBt9_ZliC_.png","title":"Lemon tart","publishedAt":"2016-10-16T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"10.7 g","fat":"39.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"46.5 g","calories":"2428 kJ \/ 578 kcal"},"usefulItems":"rectangular fluted tart tin (34 x 13 cm), bowl, serving platter, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Place baked tart into preheated oven (170°C) on a baking tray before carefully pouring filling into it to avoid spilling."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","2h 25m","6 portions"]}